text: Alta, or Áltá, is a municipality in Norway's northernmost county, Finnmark. Settlements include the town of Alta. ==Administration== The municipal council is elected until late 2027. *9 council members are from Progress partyhttps://www.nrk.no/valg/2023/resultat/fylke/56/5601.
